HEADWORD: Coromandel
<hw>Cor`o*man"del</hw> <pr>(k?r`?-m?n"d<it>e</it>l)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Geol.)</fld> <def>The west coast, or a portion of the west coast,
of the Bay of Bengal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Coromandel gooseberry</b></col>. <cd>See
